{
  "stem": "5837.1",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So in other words, even though those people probably got attached to those-- to those kids, I'm sure that the people that raised me, that Polish family, maybe they didn't want to give me back.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I wouldn't be surprised.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "After all, I spent with them quite a few years, and I came there just as a baby.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But there was a law that required them to return those Jewish kids.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I imagine that that's how-- I-- I imagine that when my parents survived, there was a Jewish community center, where everybody that survived would come and write their name on the big board, and then people would come there and see who's alive, who's not, and-- and I guess this is how they inquired-- they-- they wanted me returned.",
      "word_count": 60
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You know?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And so I was brought to the Jewish orphanage.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You know why they brought you to the Jewish orphanage?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I think they brought me there because my mother was there, and she wanted--",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My real mother, yes.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] You know--",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, she was very sweet, and she gave me a lot of attention.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And she talked to me, and then eventually she said that she's going to-- she's taking me home.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't remember exactly when it happened, but I do remember her telling me that.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And you know, with all the things that were happening in my life, I mean, I don't know.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It just-- things were just happening, you know?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "As a matter of fact, you know, later on, in Israel, and I was talking to people, all kinds of little-- little things came up that-- I remember, somebody told me in Israel, what makes you think that these are really your parents?",
      "word_count": 43
    }
  ],
